name: analytic
caption: Analytic

effect.short: Strengthens moves to 1.3× their power when moving last.
effect.full:
This Pokémon's moves have 1.3× their power when it moves last in a turn.

[]{move:future-sight} and []{move:doom-desire} are unaffected.

flavorText: Boosts move power when the Pokémon moves last.
